t Skill** вҖ” Update to use MCP wrapper (replacing OAuth flow)\\nрҹ”ө **BE Notification System** вҖ” Local behind remote by 11 commits; notification system feature pending merge\\n\\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\\n\\n**3пёҸвғЈ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\\n\\nвҡ пёҸ **BE Merge Conflict** вҖ” Backend is 11 commits behind remote on `notification-system`; remote is 2 commits ahead on `data-isolation`. **Lead decision required** before merge can proceed.\\n\\nвҡ пёҸ **Context Overflow Risk** вҖ” Session crash root cause identified (200k+ tokens / model instability). Monitor session health closely.\\n\\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\\n\\n**Pipeline Status:** рҹҹў HEALTHY\\n**Active Agents:** 34 (v4 ecosystem)\\n**Active Session:** telegram:group:-5212380728\\n\\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\\nOrbis рҹҢҗ вҖ” Global Orchestrator\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 328,\n            \"output\": 570,\n            \"totalTokens\": 17958,\n            \"cacheRead\": 14121,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 2939,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776117671474,\n          \"responseId\": \"062c9aa87844c59bbd285766e62b966f\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"faf39631\",\n            \"seq\": 7\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}[... 25686 more characters truncated]"}],"details":{"count":20,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"label":"Cron: 5p Progress Report","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7","deliveryCon