5AM UTC+7","displayName":"Cron: Daily Briefing 5AM UTC+7","updatedAt":1776117647627,"sessionId":"ea4aae72-5a80-46e3-9664-b4f085f6b8ff","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":17388,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/ea4aae72-5a80-46e3-9664-b4f085f6b8ff.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough context to compose the daily briefing. Let me craft a clean status report for the Telegram group -5212380728.\n\nKey info:\n- Yesterday (2026-04-12): AHV Works review complete, session crash and recovery, BE behind 11 commits, FE synced\n- Today (2026-04-13): Fix AHV Works P0 issues (13 items), Stitch MCP wrapper test, stitch-connect skill update, BE merge decision pending\n- Blockers: BE is 11 commits behind remote on notification system, Lead decision needed for merge\n\nCurrent time is 10:00 PM UTC (10:00 PM Monday April 13), so this briefing covers the day and sets up for Tuesday.\n\n\nNow I'll format this as a status report."},{"type":"text","text":"рҹҢ… **ORBIS MORNING BRIEFING**\nрҹ“… Monday, April 13, 2026\nвҸ° 10:00 PM UTC | 5:00 AM UTC+7\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\n\n**1пёҸвғЈ YESTERDAY'S COMPLETED TASKS**\n\nвң… **AHV Works Review** вҖ” FULL REVIEW COMPLETE (commit 84cdb2d)\nвң… **Session Recovery** вҖ” Crash at 00:34 UTC (HTTP 500 / context overflow), fully recovered on model `AHV-Holding-DEV`\nвң… **FE Sync** вҖ” Frontend fully synchronized with remote develop вң…\nвң… **DTLX/QLHV Systems** вҖ” Stable, shared DB architecture operational\nвң… **34-Agent Ecosystem** вҖ” SKILL_GATES, HANDOVER/FEEDBACK, OPENSPEC all verified вң…\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\n\n**2пёҸвғЈ TODAY'S PRIORITIES**\n\nрҹ”ҙ **P0 вҖ” AHV Works Fixes** вҖ” 13 unresolved P0 issues queued for resolution\nрҹҹЎ **Stitch MCP Wrapper** вҖ” Complete integration testing post-gateway restart\nрҹҹЎ **stitch-connect Skill** вҖ” Update to use MCP wrapper (replacing OAuth flow)\nрҹ”ө **BE Notification System** вҖ” Local behind remote by 11 commits; notification system feature pending merge\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\n\n**3пёҸвғЈ BLOCKERS & RISKS**\n\nвҡ пёҸ **BE Merge Conflict** вҖ” Backend is 11 commits behind remote on `notification-system`; remote is 2 commits ahead on `data-isolation`. **Lead decision required** before merge can proceed.\n\nвҡ пёҸ **Context Overflow Risk** вҖ” Session crash root cause identified (200k+ tokens / model instability). Monitor session health closely.\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\n\n**Pipeline Status:** рҹҹў HEALTHY\n**Active Agents:** 34 (v4 ecosystem)\n**Active Session:** telegram:group:-5212380728\n\nв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\nOrbis рҹҢҗ вҖ” Global Orchestrator"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":328,"output":570,"totalTokens":17958,"cacheRead":14121,"cacheWrite":2939,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776117671474,"responseId":"062c9aa87844c59bbd285766e62b966f","__openclaw":{"id":"faf39631","seq":7}}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1776193175042}}
