HV (SUBSYSTEM)\\n   Hб»Ү thб»‘ng chГӯnh                    TГЎch ra cho THбәҰY/GV\\n   Ban giГЎm Д‘б»‘c, Sales, Admin        GiГЎo viГӘn quбәЈn lГҪ HV\\n        в”Ӯ                                 в”Ӯ\\n        в””в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ SHARED MONGODB в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҳ\\n              103.253.21.98:27017\\n```\\n\\n**вҶ’ QLHV phбәЈi Д‘б»“ng bб»ҷ dб»Ҝ liб»Үu vб»ӣi DTLX luГҙn luГҙn.**\\n**вҶ’ Khi dev QLHV, phбәЈi HIб»ӮU DTLX schema vГ¬ cГ№ng DB.**\\n\\n## Project Identity\\n- **DTLX Name**: AHV DTLX (ДҗГ o TбәЎo LГЎi Xe) вҖ” MASTER\\n- **QLHV Name**: AHV QLHV (QuбәЈn LГҪ Hб»Қc ViГӘn) вҖ” SUBSYSTEM\\n- **Telegram\\n\\nSource: memory/dtlx-context.md#L1-L46\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/dtlx-context.md#L1-L46\",\n      \"corpus\": \"memory\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"6d33dcbcde98902d6f184f316670fd98825cd1bfa92d0d558a8ab236984c0dee\",\n      \"path\": \"memory/dtlx-context.md\",\n      \"startLine\": 38,\n      \"endLine\": 60,\n      \"score\": 0.7101868467038716,\n      \"textScore\": 0.7101868467038716,\n      \"snippet\": \"### Bб»ҷ 2: Ecosystem (ahv-qlhv/*) вҖ” ДҗANG DEV TRONG SESSION NГҖY\\n- `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-be` (id: 81078323) вҖ” Last: 2026-04-11 вң…\\n- `ahv-dtlx/ahv-qlhv-fe` (id: 81078350) вҖ” Last: 2026-04-11 вң…\\n- Дҗang hoбәЎt Д‘б»ҷng: develop + main\\n\\n### Landing Page (khГҙng Д‘б»Қc)\\n- `ahv-dtlx/ahv-landing-page-v2` (id: 80400174)\\n\\n## Local Workspace (QLHV вҖ” Д‘ang dev)\\n- **BE**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/teacher-driving-training-system.bootstrap-backup/ahv-qlhv-be/`\\n- **FE**: `/root/.openclaw/workspaces/ahv-driving-training-system/`\\n\\n## Database\\n- **MongoDB**: `mongodb://103.253.21.98:27017` (SHARED vб»ӣi DTLX)\\n- **ERD**: Confluence page `23494657` (v35) вҖ” 20+ entities\\n\\n## Agents\\n- Use prefix `ahv-dtlx:` for all spawned subagents\\n\\nSource: memory/dtlx-context.md#L38-L60\",\n      \"source\": \"memory\",\n      \"citation\": \"memory/dtlx-context.md#L38-L60\",\n      \"